{"tid":1788664,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"撕一貼百 人人有責 重建連龍 刻不容援","createTime":"2019-12-19T00:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T09:33:39.000Z","uid":187274,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"33f0b58cd4dbe74a90994f6b0bb4f90cba837f29","tid":1788664,"uid":187274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T00:45:44.000Z","msg":"A5 A4 A3 黑白 彩色 單面 雙面 高質 低質 都唔緊要！<br />\n<br />\n最緊要唔該各位而家Print定幾張，有財力就買罐噴膠，冇財力就共膠紙，再冇財力就噴漆，再冇財力扮落街食糖水放哨都得！總知今晚自已貼，晚晚都貼！<br />\n<br />\n文宣，Memo紙，老豆搵仔，仔搵老豆老母，報紙 乜都好<br />\n<br />\n天下武功唯快不破，幾張貼完即走<br />\n<br />\n唔print都寫幾張Memo紙啊<br />\n<br />\n沉默的大多數個個以為場運動完左啊！<br />\n<br />\n沉默的大多數個個以為香港人投左降啊！<br />\n<br />\n仆街政府搵人清就清飽佢，洗地車，油漆工，幾隻綠曱甴，幾個收利事廢老，行動統籬籌，交通，物料&hellip;加加埋埋政府清一個位要10幾萬，我地重新貼過洗唔洗10萬？貼1000蚊都有排佢清！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mtCBwOv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmtCBwOv.jpg&h=a28c52b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DTvvBfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDTvvBfb.jpg&h=3e80a504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/avzz2Vc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Favzz2Vc.jpg&h=bfa7d79d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Q887mS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Q887mS.jpg&h=5652ffac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oDDw48y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoDDw48y.jpg&h=515175f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7GDMT1T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7GDMT1T.jpg&h=2d3b1aa7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PDiMT1U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPDiMT1U.jpg&h=33d58908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4A4wkGV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail